info.title: Dream A Little Dream Of Me

metadata.album: Carry On Up The Charts: The Best Of The Beautiful South

lines.text: stars shining bright above you
night breezes seem to whisper "i love you"
birds singing in the sycamore tree
dream a little dream of me
say "nighty night" and kiss me
just hold me tight
and tell me you'll miss me
while i'm alone and blue as can be
dream a little dream of me
stars fading, but i linger on dear,
still craving your kiss
i'm longing to linger til dawn, dear
just saying this
sweet dreams til sun beams find you
sweet dreams that leave
our worries behind you
but in your dreams, whatever they be
dream a little dream of me

that leave our worries-far behind you

dream a little dream of me
